      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very sound, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience with a responsive engine and solid transmission. While there may be minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, the interior is clean and the exterior retains a strong appearance. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
