      "description": "We are pleased to present this collector-grade vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This example represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in peerless condition, exhibiting virtually no wear and a documented history of meticulous care. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. This is a vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands excellence.",
